OL,7,FTom Barton speaks to the mother of
OL,8,FHolly Newton about her plans to raise
OL,9,Fmoney for bleed kits across
OL,10,FNorthumberland.
OL,12,FThe mother of a teenager who was
OL,13,Fstabbed in Northumberland is raising
OL,14,Fmoney for equipment that could help
OL,15,Fprevent further tragedies.
OL,17,FHolly Newton, 15, of Haltwhistle, in
OL,18,FHexham in January 2023.
