OL,4,CNewton fundraise for bleed kits in her
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,FHolly's mother Micala Trussler said:
OL,8,F"I remember sitting in the hospital
OL,9,Fand kind of thinking 'this doesn't
OL,10,Fhappen to us'. Not believing what was
OL,11,Fhappening to us.
OL,13,F"It's the worst night of any parent's
OL,14,Flife, having to hear that."
OL,16,FHolly's family has now launched a non-
OL,17,Fprofit organisation called Holly's
OL,18,FHope, and are fundraising to provide
OL,19,Fbleed kits to help save the lives of
OL,20,Fpeople who have suffered a traumatic
OL,21,Finjury.
