OL,7,FThe emergency kits contain equipment
OL,8,Fwhich can help a bystander to stop
OL,9,Fpotentially life-threatening bleeding
OL,10,Funtil paramedics arrive.
OL,12,FMs Trussler told ITV Tyne Tees: "We
OL,13,Fsettled on Holly's Hope because it's
OL,14,Four hope to save somebody's life in
OL,15,FHolly's name.
