OL,3,CFamily of stabbed teenager Holly
OL,4,CNewton fundraise for bleed kits in her
OL,5,Cmemory
OL,7,F"(It would mean) that we've achieved
OL,8,Fsomething, in Holly's name. That
OL,9,FHolly's memory is still alive.
OL,10,FHonestly, I'll feel amazing if we can
OL,11,Fsave just one life. We might never get
OL,12,Fto find out but I'm okay with that. I
OL,13,Flike to feel that we've contributed."
OL,15,FSpeaking of life since losing her
OL,16,Fdaughter, Ms Trussler, who has three
OL,17,Fother children, said: "Every day is
OL,18,Fawful. You get up and you get on. I
OL,19,Fhave other kids that need me. Inside,
OL,20,Fyou're actually still a mess.
